11771  const float* get_mit_hrtf_2D(unsigned long samplerate, unsigned long azimuth)
11772  {
11773  int number_of_samples;
11774  int azimuth_offset;
11775 
11776  if(samplerate == 44100)
11777  number_of_samples = 512;
11778  else if(samplerate == 48000)
11779  number_of_samples = 557;
11780  else if(samplerate == 88200)
11781  number_of_samples = 1024;
11782  else if(samplerate == 96000)
11783  number_of_samples = 1114;
11784  else
11785  return NULL;
11786 
11787  if(azimuth % 5 != 0)
11788  {
11789  if(azimuth > 356)
11790  azimuth = 0;
11791  else if(azimuth % 5 < 3)
11792  azimuth -= azimuth % 5;
11793  else
11794  azimuth += azimuth % 5;
11795  }
11796  azimuth_offset = azimuth / 5 * number_of_samples;
11797 
11798  if(samplerate == 44100)
11799  return MIT_HRTF_44100+azimuth_offset;
11800  else if(samplerate == 48000)
11801  return MIT_HRTF_48000+azimuth_offset;
11802  else if(samplerate == 88200)
11803  return MIT_HRTF_88200+azimuth_offset;
11804  else if(samplerate == 96000)
11805  return MIT_HRTF_96000+azimuth_offset;
11806  return NULL;
11807  }
